# Weather God

##Description
A minimalistic weather app for Android.

##Features
1. Includes Material Design.
2. Detects user location when GPS is enabled.
3. User can provide any location of his choice when GPS is disabled.
4. Includes Auto Refresh.
4. Temparature charts for the daily and weekly forecasts.
5. Allows user to choose between Dark and Light theme.
6. Along with theme, user can choose the theme foreground color of his choice from the list.

